data.description:
POOL HOME!  Note lot size!!!  Home shows very nicely, with an open floor plan, cathedral ceilings, crown moldings and 6" base.  Front porch is screened and tiled.  Garage is large and is wired for generator.  Master bath has walk in shower and double vanity.   AC new in 2020.  Disposal was new in 2021 refrigerator, stove, dishwasher, counters, sink and faucet all new in 2018.  All light fixtures and fans were also replaced at that time.  Interior was freshly painted in 2021.  Custom blinds were added in 2021. Some of the screens in the back porch have been replaced this year as well as some of the bushes.  It's ready to move into!
Adjacent vacant lot included in purchase!
